    "ScoringStrategy.",
    "In the \"Scoring Strategy\", we ask the LLM to assign a score to each explanation for a window 𝑤 using the Likert scale [11] (i.e., a score between 1 and 5).",
    "When the same explanation is generated by more than one model in 𝐻, we assign the same score to all the models that generated that explanation.",
    "At the end of this process, the model in 𝐻 with the highest score is considered as the best.",
    "The prompt.Figure 1 shows the system prompts (i.e., the instructions for the LLM to perform the task) of our approach."
  ],
